<HEADLINE> Karachi Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, June 11 (Xinhua) -- The Karachi Stock Exchange
KSE-100 Index today decreased by 18.33 points and closed at
1587.60 points.
</P>
<P>
The total turnover today was 41.08 million shares as against
the turnover of 37.85 million shares Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Total shares of 332 companies were traded today. Share prices
of 73 companies went up, those of 201 companies went down, while
share prices of 58 companies remained unchanged.  
