All-China Federation of Industry and Commerce; non-party personage
Cheng Siyuan; as well as Tung Chee Hwa, first chief executive of
the Hong Kong SAR.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, members of the delegation include officials with the
Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee, the National
People's Congress (NPC), the State Council, the Chinese People's
Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) National Committee, the
Central Military Commission, and representatives of people's
organizations.  
