<HEADLINE> Industrial Output Increases In Brazil </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Brazil's industrial
production increased 5.5 percent during the first five months of
this year over the same period of last year, said the Brazilian
Institute of Geography and Statistics (IBGE).
</P>
<P>
